description._content: Description: kharg Island from which supplies of stone for Abadan are drawn_two of the Company's barges sunk in a storm appear in the picture. Location: Kharg Island, Persia Description: Approaching Ganawah on a motor mahala. Location: Ganawah, Persia Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/714 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
